</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h4>Context:</h4>
      <p>I've tried a lot of inventory management applications but all of them don't accomplish why supply chain managers want an inventory management software to begin with, which is to solve either a) a low stock problem (leading to lost revenue) or b) a high stock problem (leading to the sunk cost problem). Such need requires a metric called "Days on Hand" which equips the user with the knowledge on when s/he needs to restock and how much he needs to push demand. Hence, this project.</p>
